nk target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fa03898a23b6286eb3891b272ea34a45f2d86ade","tid":1913010,"uid":198241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5488717cb0c5725b43f16a19133f3dc2f485bb1","tid":1913010,"uid":235547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10874ce686176aef3eb683b1e8199efdab03b9e6","tid":1913010,"uid":198241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be97ed64ee79e02b5ef400e80d67a1585fa4e69d","tid":1913010,"uid":76370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:43:30.000Z","msg":"E mini? cme?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:44:35.000Z","msg":"why not?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:46:51.000Z","msg":"家境清貧, UPRO 可以一股一股咁買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:50:46.000Z","msg":"~3000 x 50 USD 係nominal value <br />\n賭緊150000usd <br />\n其實大少少啦<br />\n你3倍速 嘅話，買50000usd upro 就係e mini <br />\n不過都真係唔少<br />\n長買upro 無著數<br />\nleverage decay 蝕死<br />\nfuture 自己操盤，靈活性大d"},{"pid":"d6decf78e23e9acad9fc0300b11cd0c6c791ef26","tid":1913010,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:58:16.000Z","msg":"真心希望樓豬贏錢離場<br />\n否則下次點 tum 到佢輸身家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c94aa5053638dc70c0857aa3feaab764062420","tid":1913010,"uid":211993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:59:51.000Z","msg":"有錢就是任性"},{"pid":"165eb9588e4db7eecb6f5a5441e0003cfc7e8f31","tid":1913010,"uid":5777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:00:16.000Z","msg":"你要溝3次貨 已經證明